title: Hoshigari Hime no Bouken
synopsis: A fairy-tale telling the story of a wealthy, spoiled princess Katharine who got changed into "normal" girl by a Witch and now have to live among common village folks adapting to their modest lifestyle.
related_anime: ['UFO Nitsukamatta Kodomo-tachi', 'Hyakumannen Attara, Dousuru?', 'Okane wa Mawaru: Kurashi to Kinyuu']
